  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/2020/09/16/where-test-driven-development-falls-short-find-a-good-repl/#content&quot;&gt;Where TDD falls short, find yourself a good REPL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
